100
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,870
Váš syn s vámi nemůže.

101
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,690
Proč?

102
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:38,280
<i>22letý muž.</i>

103
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,950
