163
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,630
Co se děje?

164
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,090
<i>Tep vyskočil na 126.</i>

165
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,410
Krvácí víc?

166
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:45,170
<i>Ne.</i>

167
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:46,750
<i>Tlak je 75.</i>

168
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,020
<i>Dostává se do šoku.</i>

169
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,530
Nedošlo k otoku plic?

170
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:53,290
<i>Ne.</i>

171
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,260
- Poslechni si ji.
- Ano.

172
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,620
<i>Není to k ničemu!</i>

173
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,160
<i>Přes hluk helikoptéry nic neslyším.</i>

